% memory_stream_snapshot_thaw.trx -- phase 2: thaw the image produced
% by tests/test_memory_stream_snapshot.trx.  The image's post-snapshot
% section re-runs after thaw and re-reads the borrowed memory-stream's
% unread tail, asserting byte-exact equality with the expected suffix.
% Run tests/test_memory_stream_snapshot.trx first to produce the image.
(tests/memory_stream_snapshot.img) thaw
